WEBVTT

00:10:29.971 --> 00:10:31.232
You know, a few years ago,

00:10:31.256 --> 00:10:35.598
when we announced that we are giving
shares to all our 2,000 employees,

00:10:35.622 --> 00:10:40.206
some people said it's PR,
some said it's a gift.

00:10:40.230 --> 00:10:41.830
I said, it's not a gift.

00:10:43.341 --> 00:10:45.872
I watched it, I've been part of it.

00:10:45.896 --> 00:10:48.623
They earned it with their talent
and with their hard work,

00:10:48.637 --> 00:10:50.219
and I don't see any other way.

00:10:51.315 --> 00:10:53.307
The new way of business --

00:10:53.331 --> 00:10:55.782
it's your employees
you take care of first.

00:10:56.692 --> 00:10:57.993
Not the profits.